<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Modern Mixology Masterclasses</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/terminal.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/layout.css">
</head>
<body>

<%- include('partials/header') %>

    <div class="terminal-container">
        <header>
            <h1>Welcome Back, <%= username %></h1>
            <p>The laboratory instruments are calibrated and awaiting your directives.</p>
        </header>

        <main>

            <section class="field-guide-section">
                <h2 class="guide-section-title">🔬 The Alchemist's Field Guide</h2>

                <div class="guide-grid">

                    <div class="guide-card">
                        <h3 class="guide-card-title">📊 Stratification</h3>
                        <p class="guide-card-text">
                            Manipulates liquid sugar weight (Brix scale) and alcohol densities to build distinct, un-mixed floating layers inside a single glassware vessel.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="guide-card">
                        <h3 class="guide-card-title">🔮 Encapsulation</h3>
                        <p class="guide-card-text">
                            Employs calcium alginate gel cross-linking to trap liquid payloads inside fragile spheres that burst with explosive flavor clarity upon consumption.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="guide-card">
                        <h3 class="guide-card-title">🧪 Acid-Adjustment</h3>
                        <p class="guide-card-text">
                            Alters the chemical pH balance of standard organic juices with precise powder vectors, synthesizing the high-acidity characteristics of citrus targets.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="guide-card">
                        <h3 class="guide-card-title">🌿 Botanical Alchemy</h3>
                        <p class="guide-card-text">
                            Accelerates solvent extraction to isolate essential oils and organic chemical compounds from root and herbal matrices into custom aromatics.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </section>

            <h2 style="color: var(--accent-blue); font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--glass-border); padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 2rem;">The Main Stage: Theatrics</h2>
            
            <div class="module-grid" style="margin-bottom: 4rem;">
                <a href="/modules/ph-shift" class="module-card">
                    <h3>Botanical Alchemy</h3>
                    <p>Master the interactive pH color shift using Butterfly Pea blossoms and citrus.</p>
                </a>
                
                <a href="/modules/spherification" class="module-card">
                    <h3>Encapsulation</h3>
                    <p>Use sodium alginate to turn liquid modifiers into bursting, edible caviar.</p>
                </a>
            </div>

            <h2 style="color: var(--accent-blue); font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--glass-border); padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 2rem;">The Prep Lab: Foundations</h2>
            
            <div class="module-grid">
                <a href="/modules/density" class="module-card">
                    <h3>Density & Stratification</h3>
                    <p>Learn the mechanics of floating spirits to create striking visual gradients.</p>
                </a>

                <a href="/modules/acid" class="module-card"> <h3>Acid-Adjustment</h3>
                    <p>Engineer citrus profiles, turning simple juices into a perfectly balanced backbone.</p>
                </a>

                <a href="/modules/pantry" class="module-card">
                    <h3>The Pantry Engine</h3>
                    <p>Select your available reagents and let the AI formulate a custom molecular protocol.</p>
                </a>


            </div>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 4rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--glass-border); font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--accent-blue); font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 1px;">
                The Archives: Record & Review
            </h2>

            <div class="module-grid">
                <a href="/modules/journal" class="module-card">
                    <h3>Laboratory Journal</h3>
                    <p>Access your personal grimoire. Review successfully formulated protocols, chemical syntheses, and past alchemical discoveries.</p>
                </a>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>
</body>
</html>